Star Ruby 0.1.13 (2008-01-27)


* About Star Ruby

Star Ruby is a ruby extensional library for creating games.
You can develop SNES-like 2D games with Star Ruby.


* Dependent Libraries

  - Fontconfig (Optional)
  - libfreetype
  - libpng
  - libogg
  - libruby
  - libvorbis
  - libvorbisfile
  - SDL
  - SDL_mixer
  - SDL_ttf
  - SMPEG
  - zlib


* How to Install

  $ ruby extconf.rb [--with-opt-dir=DIRECTORY]
  $ make
  $ make install


